reviewText: It was my first introduction to the white lion.  I know there are much better movies now, but I'm glad I finally got it.  It was hard to find.  Arrived in great shape!
Before there was Simba there was Kimba. Great anima.

Gorgeous animated movie about one of my favorite animated characters, Leo! The captioning was good, very readable, and this new movie was just great and compelling. My entire family loved it. Two thumbs up for the seller, it was in great shape and arrived fast for an overseas shipment!
